    "description": "「当你周围的世界正在燃烧时，你会做什么来拯救你仅存的最后一个地方？”」<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2333410/extras/d5b1e30f68dba8c2db9f6a745717099c.poster.avif?t=1756750215\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2333410/extras/d5b1e30f68dba8c2db9f6a745717099c.webm?t=1756750215\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2333410/extras/d5b1e30f68dba8c2db9f6a745717099c.mp4?t=1756750215\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>战术回合制角色扮演游戏</strong><br>《武装少女》是一款带有角色扮演游戏和视觉小说元素的战术回合制射击游戏。帮助一群台湾女学生努力保护学校和同学的安全，同时对抗世界各地未知且看似势不可挡的军队。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2333410/extras/e2a6f042dd4a9c76caf8b47087f54d2c.poster.avif?t=1756750215\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2333410/extras/e2a6f042dd4a9c76caf8b47087f54d2c.webm?t=1756750215\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2333410/extras/e2a6f042dd4a9c76caf8b47087f54d2c.mp4?t=1756750215\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>独特的战斗系统</strong><br>一切尽在您的掌控之中！使用不依赖机率的创新战斗系统，帮助女孩们在许多手工制作的关卡中战斗并生存。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2333410/extras/c43766449ba605e06f9868c29a21725c.poster.avif?t=1756750215\" width=600 height=376 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2333410/extras/c43766449ba605e06f9868c29a21725c.webm?t=1756750215\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2333410/extras/c43766449ba605e06f9868c29a21725c.mp4?t=1756750215\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>适应和定制</strong><br>获得强大的升级，您可以应用这些升级来帮助您在每次遭遇中生存。找到隐藏的合成组合来获得对敌人的优势。为女孩们穿上可解锁的服装并拍摄她们的照片。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2333410/extras/c7cc6bf6d58d86c610bc2df6b9964752.poster.avif?t=1756750215\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2333410/extras/c7cc6bf6d58d86c610bc2df6b9964752.webm?t=1756750215\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2333410/extras/c7cc6bf6d58d86c610bc2df6b9964752.mp4?t=1756750215\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>惊心动魄的神秘神秘故事</strong><br>跟随一个曲折的戏剧性故事，每个女孩都试图面对自己所处的新处境。随着事情变得更加黑暗和绝望，女孩们将发现比她们以前所知道的更深层次的现实以及居住的恐怖在那里。<br><br>引导他们找到最终的启示，这可能是他们唯一的救赎。",
